1. Open Terminal
2. Type: mkdir grubimage
3. Type: cd grubimage
4. Type: mkdir source
5. Place all picture with "png" format in source folder.
6. Now type: sudo gedit /etc/default/grub
    a. Add the following line:
        GRUB_BACKGROUND=/path/filename 
    b.Example: GRUB_BACKGROUND="/home/yourusername/grubimage/1.png"
7. Type: sudo update-grub
8. Now place python script to startup menu !!! 



